  m_text: "Hello? Are you there, 0419? Listen\u2026\u2026Your mission is to collect
    plant samples on this Alien Island. Be careful! These plants all have some strange
    toxicity. Don't get hurt and come back alive! Keep in mind\u2014\u2014the mission
    is completed only when you collect ALL samples!\r\nWhen you are ready, tab anywhere
    to start!"
